{"tid":973090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保安版李宗瑞！ 動物用麻藥迷昏性侵2少女　","createTime":"2019-01-08T00:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T09:15:32.000Z","uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2f4ef701e67b2047fd4a532ad5b056c5eaa07996","tid":973090,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T00:48:19.000Z","msg":"太惡劣的行徑，為了自己一時之慾，毀了2個少女的人生！請求法官重判！！！<br />\n《中國時報》報導，某保全公司區經理的羅育祥，負責公司面試工作，竟伺機在人力銀行網站搜尋急需打工求職之未成年少女，再以打工面試為由，於去年5月間結識2名年僅15、16歲的國中女，知悉2女涉世未深，且均有經濟壓力，欲下手迷昏性侵2女。<br />\n<br />\n去年5月5日，羅邀約其中1少女到住處，以拍攝實習照片為由，開車載少女返家，伺機將含有medetomidine的動物用麻醉藥品摻入飲料中，待少女因藥效發作昏迷後，加以性侵並拍猥褻照片。之後，羅又以相同的手法對另名少女下手，事後，少女父親懷疑女兒遭下藥性侵，陪女兒赴醫院採證驗傷，並報警處理。台北地檢署昨依《刑法》對少年犯以藥劑為加強性交等罪嫌起訴羅男。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190108/1496659/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190108%2F1496659%2F&d=0g%2Bqkt12DDtyN51eMBLZFC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=f2ae9f1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190108%2F1496659%2F&h=bdedb965\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190108/1496659/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66435605ba44d6bf69915c21d34e9846b1a0b2a6","tid":973090,"uid":4942,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T00:50:42.000Z","msg":"仲以為有隻動物性侵少女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98718d3de355f44a371bb272786ce7941f5f033d","tid":973090,"uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"66435605ba44d6bf69915c21d34e9846b1a0b2a6","tid":973090,"uid":4942,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T00:50:42.000Z","msg":"仲以為有隻動物性侵少女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T00:52:35.000Z","msg":"台灣不出奇"},{"pid":"1bd6fda84c689fdf48c14fd5c8ea0434489c297c","tid":973090,"u